{"id":"29b0aa020ef74d22616dd7e0a9c3008cb06c6c5e92e89d40d163e9a8344cb968","item_id":"f5fc4f9a29:0","text":"为任务选择合适的工具"}
{"id":"e57f427fbc358eb5fd7d9bb509ad5f13c48ee8a6e2bbd2b8824233412138841e","item_id":"f5fc4f9a29:1","text":"一般来说，"}
{"id":"f661ae3fa44b99f39a3606f1d1e40de7182d940f50e06252408a8338c574cbe9","item_id":"f5fc4f9a29:3","text":"有很多优势，但有时确实需要使用多边形网格。"}
{"id":"a5fef654c08215d02d095b1e1c0b274a3fda1214fb383d82d91b9a755de356eb","item_id":"f5fc4f9a29:4","text":"细分曲面"}
{"id":"d49dbef4d9086119d6ed0aa217328a66ab3d0defdf13a8c1c86282ac33152a61","item_id":"f5fc4f9a29:5","text":"优点"}
{"id":"1ce0ac4ef90fb0df45b4d4aa31fc93bc06c7e55afae87266bcb9574513143ece","item_id":"f5fc4f9a29:6","text":"在任意分辨率下都能保持完全平滑。"}
{"id":"1d6157c1b6555767dc058312cbf587bd7f0a09fb55fabf9b6114c980fb594c92","item_id":"f5fc4f9a29:25","text":"优点"}
{"id":"17b418cb3d3fc56eb27b3269a8a965043efbc58e8c423d45916a7b8d2ce64818","item_id":"f5fc4f9a29:26","text":"在任意分辨率下都能保持完全平滑。"}
{"id":"92334aee9dce568ba9d55f4a5e90729318e62e10df7cb8fdc403a2dc428d08aa","item_id":"f5fc4f9a29:7","text":"可以通过折痕和角点实现锐利或半锐利特征。"}
{"id":"a1060428f9f00b899299e83b0c2c0e1d540d01ac138cb016a9b680c34e1e64ea","item_id":"f5fc4f9a29:8","text":"内存占用可以非常轻量。"}
{"id":"fa75d99ac43067e66d4d5a0674cc8a9c34b079ec394b07f08bb5a1d54f9707fe","item_id":"f5fc4f9a29:9","text":"置换裂缝更少（水密）。"}
{"id":"5c5c68f419f2c429c5432556484a9d8200eb3aec8d5bd729cc45578a9ba61efa","item_id":"f5fc4f9a29:10","text":"缺点"}
{"id":"4efb04a15d564ccb6d50bba135b06b3e12cce121b0569009939ecda8610b7fdc","item_id":"f5fc4f9a29:28","text":"缺点"}
{"id":"2e86336f85fbfb0999a134064f93e0f7fc76743dfaaae986ef23b2b063b6a89f","item_id":"f5fc4f9a29:11","text":"需要不同的建模技术/技能。"}
{"id":"2babda63e8c50076c0bf4532908e23b02b054effefb864021e3a8ef968b5ee09","item_id":"f5fc4f9a29:12","text":"需要标记锐利边和顶点。"}
{"id":"ab627e21d55d9bde3eb96cd8347a2ceb5d8ac628848cc63af3ab0c130e6d893f","item_id":"f5fc4f9a29:13","text":"存在一些拓扑约束（四边形或三角形，不能有非流形几何体）。"}
{"id":"c18eb878c4e42e57fc5a1a7293e239ffbcf5d358019f184295e68444932390fb","item_id":"f5fc4f9a29:14","text":"多边形网格"}
{"id":"d49dbef4d9086119d6ed0aa217328a66ab3d0defdf13a8c1c86282ac33152a61","item_id":"f5fc4f9a29:15","text":"优点"}
{"id":"3fda9865c60c46fda3bc545a4ce7a13b31de7d75f8cc228565c441e629b5777d","item_id":"f5fc4f9a29:95","text":"多边形网格"}
{"id":"067192ce182b804896c76f76b6fd9355b1909ebc9bacfbf54958c13bd6d8d6fa","item_id":"f5fc4f9a29:16","text":"非常适合 3D 扫描网格这类重型几何体。"}
{"id":"cbe0ffae6cadb036c849ce5263049b30aad624cb76f6a76054382630573362cd","item_id":"f5fc4f9a29:17","text":"最适合会被破碎或模拟的几何体。"}
{"id":"08ee6d9bb97e1b7ff646a24f826b1b2c7b066fbc231aa675d9b4af90f9b78b4c","item_id":"f5fc4f9a29:18","text":"适合只有锐利边且不需要置换的模型。"}
{"id":"bcf1dec2b83f358a1a17d95ca6a3d9bbe3d75a219e69a9ee81d4722d13fe49a","item_id":"f5fc4f9a29:19","text":"如果不进行置换，就不会生成微多边形。"}
{"id":"80102d9eaac577b7d0de0363a22ca291d55decefb9678d62f50610cccffc75f2","item_id":"f5fc4f9a29:21","text":"重型模型会占用大量内存，无论它们在图像中看起来多小。"}
{"id":"fd4fc3cedba62076fc255833d724cc3b3adae0225984e88dd9043d150c9d3f4d","item_id":"f5fc4f9a29:22","text":"在低分辨率的平滑对象上可能会看到阴影终止线。"}
{"id":"c7ba37b59a3ef22abed1ee6d6d8643d77214c57969700f180c1f5e75bb3a4d1f","item_id":"f5fc4f9a29:23","text":"可能会看到置换裂缝。"}
{"id":"5c5c68f419f2c429c5432556484a9d8200eb3aec8d5bd729cc45578a9ba61efa","item_id":"f5fc4f9a29:20","text":"缺点"}
{"id":"321b2069f246a72a716a59cf8a71d3d275a93c6181dc57bf0e26e269e083713f","item_id":"f5fc4f9a29:24","text":"NURBS"}
{"id":"5973de41039c8bc955c5abbe5e9a1996bd3d13ad3e2da55e52896443ee31ed65","item_id":"f5fc4f9a29:27","text":"内存占用轻量。"}
{"id":"2b0a04e648c5b928c32d34fcaafc4cc1f4e65da64f73eae65af5d24e8b8bacdf","item_id":"f5fc4f9a29:29","text":"只能使用四边形建模。"}
{"id":"c49d554c7c311aa4ddfdde516f9695967960c29c55ab13b88c98d38720d5e7d8","item_id":"f5fc4f9a29:30","text":"XPU 不支持。"}
{"id":"7e71d747d4aa240f1f60fbb04bcbe65f213950f5803789d0bec1615b8a901f9c","item_id":"f5fc4f9a29:31","text":"如今已不太常用。"}
{"id":"ca2af5230a71c0cef9d751a50b7c4e59685b3cb924974d7b74d65c604dbb10a1","item_id":"f5fc4f9a29:32","text":"推荐阅读："}
{"id":"88bf0bd182b140b1f122e8da6404ed619070cae4f0db7485d12874ebbe2f1975","item_id":"f5fc4f9a29:33","text":"几何体"}
{"id":"09da3d03abf398637e685d95784bc7b9a62f6bd2f8b2ed067ef9f643c0e0fdf4","item_id":"f5fc4f9a29:34","text":"细分曲面"}
{"id":"e4148d7cb5d8d5529d3c30b1084da5cead71b4d05a18d8cece39ce5fd55f7dc2","item_id":"f5fc4f9a29:36","text":"细分建模"}
{"id":"0d48122400fef2d72a39e1d5da721f39659337007c22f6d3b72f33b283a78bbf","item_id":"f5fc4f9a29:37","text":"始终尽可能建模出"}
{"id":"53c380f94521a9416c5d7437ea8e1ebf6db1ec10d464a75fbd5a93279e533314","item_id":"f5fc4f9a29:38","text":"最简单的控制笼"}
{"id":"32597bfb929484e90bc0c81be20b822c572673531f5a36a6e4fe6870c9c90c49","item_id":"f5fc4f9a29:39","text":"。"}
{"id":"7044c3da38fa8d6dcb2980299103ed180c16bc4b1b1cd2636c47a85ec683dcb8","item_id":"f5fc4f9a29:40","text":"始终以平滑方式查看模型，或使用"}
{"id":"a138130de4f5f5aa1d8df9bce92810dd4dd600fa9f9fc242d4f99eeb81a5bdff8","item_id":"f5fc4f9a29:41","text":"PxrVisualizer"}
{"id":"768a8bf5c7a8f7dd2e947f81c53c099db5810adad55f87498647ec9ac72a98c3","item_id":"f5fc4f9a29:43","text":"甚至可以在实时 PxrVisualizer 渲染中进行建模！"}
{"id":"bb7801ebc8d25fdf69408cce1c7b236848c55e058838f3db414cb3d8972cc26b","item_id":"f5fc4f9a29:44","text":"使用折痕来制作锐利或半锐利边，而无需添加额外的边循环。"}
{"id":"8c7f3600f58164d905e7148e279f4c4849a14a0b154484f1e14fb6910777ef78","item_id":"f5fc4f9a29:45","text":"细分折痕演示"}
{"id":"296ad28ffdb7ca4fbfbe1de6f2eb0aa3b3386d91785fc381df981c3b90bb01d4","item_id":"f5fc4f9a29:46","text":"我们选择了一个二十面体的所有边，并将它们的折痕值从 0.0 动画到 5.0。"}
{"id":"c7754fb5c06c85f8eb77be173a4051e4cdccf12fe5bd1a4a062bb143dc0b98f1","item_id":"f5fc4f9a29:47","text":"所有边都可以具有不同的折痕值，并且仍能在最终曲面上保持平滑过渡。"}
{"id":"96394c130cfaa087f283e4e6674d38c7df98c826bd91d6a1559e892f4c032982","item_id":"f5fc4f9a29:48","text":"角点对顶点的作用类似于折痕。"}
{"id":"07d1379dd50900f4b5f1885cc23646cf8685b4b799acdbd45fdb7b304a802a6","item_id":"f5fc4f9a29:49","text":"细分角点演示"}
{"id":"f695a23303cfc3f365d133b8d8f78ce4cc2c11a4b2e53ff483ef909f96a8d64a","item_id":"f5fc4f9a29:50","text":"在这段动画中，一个三角形面的 3 条边具有 5.0 的折痕值。"}
{"id":"b043197c8927977a2a0c731b82b2e49d05dd7218576855250f8bc21d531342296","item_id":"f5fc4f9a29:51","text":"我们将该三角形顶点的角点值从 0 提高到 5.0。"}
{"id":"78a9ad8021161373f952f1343b37cd9dab9a2e7a44b3003744684671d231592d","item_id":"f5fc4f9a29:52","text":"请注意收紧区域周围非常平滑的过渡。"}
{"id":"d9e75b6a43f99516202dc2c1995de0f485941552d6963dfce786b0d8cb59ab08","item_id":"f5fc4f9a29:53","text":"细分曲面有 3 种类型。"}
{"id":"d79e5f4a37b61ab763e30dec3bc2e6e435261331c47ab440b15fa99bbfdcaef5","item_id":"f5fc4f9a29:54","text":"Catmull-Clark 是最灵活也最常用的一种。"}
{"id":"bc0f60ffef1bff2f8e31d28e65479350c097a16ce0ed43209fb7910822e246c8","item_id":"f5fc4f9a29:55","text":"Loop 是基于三角形的细分曲面。"}
{"id":"ce79dfd0148f4e1e11f5ceeb5d6905885eb664a461fe39df00a7b4fcbe74daea","item_id":"f5fc4f9a29:56","text":"没有折痕或角点。"}
{"id":"29953c9b45686251f433e0a1cef271b781187699cd1c68d6bf515b2b1634d650","item_id":"f5fc4f9a29:57","text":"适用于布料模拟。"}
{"id":"21b4c93e97c48420f00117a87f539f82f6355c00b30e8e9a4784ea849fd8550d","item_id":"f5fc4f9a29:58","text":"Bilinear 类似于在所有边上具有无限硬折痕的 Catmull-Clark。"}
{"id":"1857b47ea32ef62227805e6af69ba88f44b3f8f08438d9be586651b37b54dc33","item_id":"f5fc4f9a29:59","text":"镶嵌细分"}
{"id":"4c9bb48c71a2603b045ee4abe6b3d4ecbb270ed8d41654e5952ebc53616d46bb","item_id":"f5fc4f9a29:60","text":"如果你来自需要手动设置细分级别的其他渲染器，可以忘掉那套做法："}
{"id":"a85708652e85e0d387952f6ff14b74697e1b84cc091bdc9409e96e0c93490438","item_id":"f5fc4f9a29:61","text":"曲面的镶嵌细分是自动的，"}
{"id":"f4088382eba0bde5950564d0915523ef7069e06284e3fe9467cf196ca6fcd5be6","item_id":"f5fc4f9a29:62","text":"在 RenderMan 中（我们称之为"}
{"id":"c1952b6420c4a25c56424c96a3c586fd28d934712d4ee0a780ab2585005e7b79","item_id":"f5fc4f9a29:63","text":"切分"}
{"id":"996f68023f6226e903dc4c344d7ed916a9a184d838c0ba0a14752b4fa426de66","item_id":"f5fc4f9a29:64","text":"主要控制项是"}
{"id":"8796b77340d62db38a3c7726f6ede1825f4819f7d046d9a2a467d976f8b68cc6","item_id":"f5fc4f9a29:65","text":"微多边形长度"}
{"id":"c7eebbe78091e20b3770e948c0b152808184013e54fb943ad71efc46033e7b57","item_id":"f5fc4f9a29:67","text":"默认情况下，它以像素表示；micropolygonlength 为 1（默认值）意味着每个微多边形大约为 1 像素宽。"}
{"id":"935d197fbc6790006d633c5fd2ccfeb768257d565f37e50e1d20b9c7b739e67","item_id":"f5fc4f9a29:68","text":"如果不希望镶嵌细分动态变化，可以将它设置在对象空间或世界空间中，或者定义一个切分相机。"}
{"id":"4cd14ee28325a8fc6d0f0435efdf2190bf2cf51af7aeaf736eb3753e9ff0be88","item_id":"f5fc4f9a29:69","text":"除非看到伪影，否则建议禁用 “raster-oriented dicing”。"}
{"id":"0f11a3a26402293870ca5a5c70ff16ec9f8a2fc0d3699fd0dd555f0ef3541891","item_id":"f5fc4f9a29:70","text":"细分与多边形切分演示"}
{"id":"2b166a8465ce1c009b5756fe9e6555a7f6fc5ee9573a25835ff9c8ee16f17c69","item_id":"f5fc4f9a29:71","text":"我们比较了一个带折痕和置换的 Catmull-Clark 细分曲面与一个等效的多边形网格。"}
{"id":"ccfbabcc3a5343b7b354fb8052cc409e8e49887bc87f61ec57dc44be4989b46c","item_id":"f5fc4f9a29:72","text":"增加微多边形长度等同于让对象在图像中的尺寸变小。"}
{"id":"0e19dbf91c40821cf5b1e5b50575479c6e07d2c02478b98a53bc527b8e4b8eb5","item_id":"f5fc4f9a29:73","text":"当对象很大时，它会被精细镶嵌细分为数百万个微多边形，从而显示细致的置换细节。"}
{"id":"6f1936d31358a3c0963bd3fd308af712ab29d8d3ca11cf170e88be96cf2b9104","item_id":"f5fc4f9a29:74","text":"当对象变得小于一个像素时，只会保留基础网格。"}
{"id":"876f5f4d0e223d98a1571f00c42800e0e23be1d18d9351d7319eb0b24c49f4f8","item_id":"f5fc4f9a29:75","text":"微多边形长度"}
{"id":"9b30868a36891f9331e2b7f0763d634be5f15a5d94b4cc566d9f20ccc67a64a0","item_id":"f5fc4f9a29:76","text":"有点像一种“自动细节层级”；当对象在屏幕上小到不需要完整细节表示时，它可以节省内存。"}
{"id":"2952d756285df7c2d19e63e959757dc6b5c450c576e70c11ac911f47e9d23b6d","item_id":"f5fc4f9a29:77","text":"请注意，"}
{"id":"6a34f28246f79fc1791dd12e64fa1a0d9e656d225853b3cb926f2420021d7427c","item_id":"f5fc4f9a29:78","text":"细分曲面会退化为少得多的面"}
{"id":"95311b213ae664c5f6324099f4f5afde3051f6889a6d03d86e441b8e005636b7","item_id":"f5fc4f9a29:79","text":"，从而节省内存并加快光线追踪。"}
{"id":"b38eb782ef31cece5b06a49a15453f8e6637d28507dc1c1552c8cf4c13c0a19","item_id":"f5fc4f9a29:80","text":"这就是所谓的"}
{"id":"08240bb286e69decc3f456d93ba2f68d978c700743d2cfbc66b4ba70c5639063","item_id":"f5fc4f9a29:81","text":"数据放大"}
{"id":"1fdc69edae5a7a38176b29a0fb532e077f578d29bc5a849edc56a4934ba16c7","item_id":"f5fc4f9a29:82","text":"：紧凑的几何表示可以按需扩增，以创建更多细节。"}
{"id":"a7d94f3caa7dc85bb64c5506d9b97dbd5c95b0e9624cbd0b69d4572b2b4960d","item_id":"f5fc4f9a29:83","text":"模型细节"}
{"id":"563c58f8058e79866964724aa132a61ea729dd87ce4b740a4bd2f6b41cc705775","item_id":"f5fc4f9a29:84","text":"通常，更好的做法是依靠置换和凹凸贴图来添加细节。"}
{"id":"de68c1d5e9fdf72fc3b241573145304a04fad10a237db0257c5feaf544d2217c","item_id":"f5fc4f9a29:85","text":"置换可以添加较大的几何特征，这些特征会影响对象的轮廓和投影。"}
{"id":"3e5ccf3da89a9bd159dce1adca07c315b368ee1fbf4c22dd42d92ad686f53610","item_id":"f5fc4f9a29:86","text":"置换会影响首个像素时间（微多边形生成），但不会拖慢着色。"}
{"id":"5ed9d0307b298ed84348d6f3f5aa7cfb395c8e44b94f53648f46bfa4c35d9ea1","item_id":"f5fc4f9a29:87","text":"凹凸贴图或法线贴图会添加小尺度细节。"}
{"id":"1fc33672e9e08be411384eb8a4c9a9c505a23beac3f6e0bbfe58dd2c2a45cc8","item_id":"f5fc4f9a29:88","text":"凹凸贴图会在着色期间增加少量成本（每次光线命中时都会重新计算）。"}
{"id":"a4909d24d3929e56c1f160f1dfeaa25de4a13a2ae2cca504318ea43d96f89789","item_id":"f5fc4f9a29:89","text":"请注意，如果入射光线过于“模糊”，我们的凹凸贴图节点不会计算 bump；这意味着没有 bump 也不会被注意到。"}
{"id":"bc5b1a8e601e5b5cb970f9e45c47ca53137fbb24f3ffcc707272919a76372804","item_id":"f5fc4f9a29:90","text":"如果你在 ZBrush 中建模了一个高度详细的对象，应考虑："}
{"id":"44e44e525065a0f8ecb97f47cfad2268781f3c6b612ff4aaf3cf85431137e9c0","item_id":"f5fc4f9a29:91","text":"重新拓扑以创建轻量模型"}
{"id":"71f73cce20c486e5421724c5b1ebd47bef7a8c53b9e24e727b84e6a9eb7ba19","item_id":"f5fc4f9a29:92","text":"从高分辨率网格中提取置换贴图。"}
{"id":"b7ed216571f8776269e073b07a56cfd4d08c4f8e10e40783f5ca6e4ad66e93d8","item_id":"f5fc4f9a29:93","text":"我们的置换节点具有一个 “model displacement” 输入，用于连接提取出的置换贴图。"}
{"id":"165560988372ffec2d21ea51ba98a6a150a8dab3daaf51c2e751e5806fbcdea","item_id":"f5fc4f9a29:94","text":"内存使用与性能"}
{"id":"f7c4ee7de871cc5e3000fdc2b867ce9fda2e04e379b9429523f5cf9d846b585d","item_id":"f5fc4f9a29:96","text":"如果没有置换，则"}
{"id":"106eec316560a6b95a03bf7d88efd0ba124d365e34f1f611bd63becd148958c0","item_id":"f5fc4f9a29:97","text":"首个像素时间"}
{"id":"26a395d1f01a6419d0cc9b307062eb6e981ec9367b0d51c71e5c749a2513a95","item_id":"f5fc4f9a29:98","text":"（TTFP）最短。"}
{"id":"7b703ac5ecf2ac6294ea5703c0dc031aa76d0571b6b8f234b7f8a9a0dca5","item_id":"f5fc4f9a29:99","text":"进行置换时，网格会被切分并生成微多边形。"}
{"id":"8c61c44e868c4bbd7ff0d8032489deec3672afe30c247325fba88c43501b311a","item_id":"f5fc4f9a29:100","text":"未置换的重型网格会使用相同数量的 RAM，无论它是全屏显示还是只有 2 像素高。"}
{"id":"a500a231736b3f5e36a13eef0e87f033e7c7a6b69ee8dec7a6444dbe943f278c","item_id":"f5fc4f9a29:102","text":"TTFP 略长，但切分是多线程的，且效率很高。"}
{"id":"82896c65c8bc9fc8d293e51a6815b54a4ccb7d53c211e50d2aef076ca47c3c34","item_id":"f5fc4f9a29:103","text":"在顶点数量相同的情况下，会比网格多使用一点内存。"}
{"id":"a80697822e1c107ffba1d7d2a78a03a9d8fd35f371b9cbd961373580765420ab","item_id":"f5fc4f9a29:104","text":"稀疏建模的细分曲面在只有 2 像素高时，只会包含基础网格面。"}
{"id":"44143cbd9207440146020ad31f51417fded6fa9e2ecc29b35bc5d4a75262745e0","item_id":"f5fc4f9a29:105","text":"这种自适应性会降低内存使用并加快光线追踪。"}
{"id": "c1362831054c724549ceabad5cb0f299e6a3ed4b1b3e14c67d1e9c2230f4c588", "item_id": "f5fc4f9a29:2", "text": "细分曲面"}
{"id": "04ae21153093e11a11baaf18a92a8266ce547e68d6f887e52e7b79b9766306bf", "item_id": "f5fc4f9a29:35", "text": "多边形"}
{"id": "cdb4ee2aea69cc6a83331bbe96dc2caa9a299d21329efb0336fc02a82e1839a8", "item_id": "f5fc4f9a29:42", "text": "。"}
